#: python-novice-gapminder/_episodes/09-plotting.md:133
msgid ""
">\n"
"> This can be done in `matplotlib` in two stages:\n"
"> \n"
"> * Provide a label for each dataset in the figure:\n"
">\n"
"> ~~~\n"
"> plt.plot(years, gdp_australia, label='Australia')\n"
